{
  "stem": "19055.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, and I told, my family lived here for 300 years at least.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We always felt at home, just like the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told us that we are Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always said we were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then more and more they told us, even as children, that you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then eventually when gradually things became worse and worse, when the first brutalities came, then, then you questioned, why me?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why us?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why Jews?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why, why am I different than anybody else?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why did I deserve this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the first questions came to my mind, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Would I like to be something else?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And many times, the answer was yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A child does not want to be different when you are in school and high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't belong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You, you're an outsider.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You suffer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They beat you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, they exclude.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They, they boycott you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't want to be different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All my childhood, I wanted to be a Boy Scout.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So finally, I applied.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I became a Boy Scout.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was one of my happiest days in, in childhood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the next day, a nice young man comes to me who was the son of the pharmacist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, I have bad news for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, you're out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You're fired.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You're not a Boy Scout any me-- anymore, after 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was dreaming up, up of the uniforms and the, and the neckties, and the metals, and the camping, and-- why?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the first big blow that I, I received.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What year was that?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
